Description:

ssh-execute is a powerful promise wrapper around ssh2-promise package. 
It helps to execute the ssh commands directly with the help of ssh promise exec function.

Installation:

npm i @bammadeep/ssh-execute

usage:

import SSHExecute = require('ssh-execute');

sshExecute = new SSHExecute();

this.sshUtil.executeCommand(hostname, usename, password, command);
